content.excerpt_text: Incident began at 2025-07-18 07:42 and ended at 2025-07-18 09:47 (all times are US/Pacific ). # Incident Report ## Summary On Friday, 18 July 2025 07:50 US/Pacific, several Google Cloud Platform (GCP) and Google Workspace (GWS) products experienced elevated latencies and error rates in the us-east1 region for a duration of up to 1 hour and 57 minutes.
